dct_title_s: Rutgers University Heights, Piscataway, New Jersey 1963
dct_description_sm: Topographic map of a portion of the Rutgers University Campus, University Heights interim dorm area from June 1963 (Piscataway Township, N.J.). Legend indicates types of foliage, construction apparatus and recreation areas.
